data.description: Location! NO FLOOD ZONE which means NO FLOOD INSURANCE,NO HOA Fees to pay,NO Assessments ALL Assessments PAID,NO Hurricane IAN Damage, Roof in perfect condition only 8 years old!This 2015 home is in The Highly Rare and Desirable Palmetto Pines Golf and Country Club Neighborhood.This charming one owner home has been taken care of so well it feels like a new home.The rear of the home faces SOUTH which is very important because during winter months the sun is in the south side of the house from sunrise to sunset so it’s nice and warm during winter. So you'll enjoy warmth relaxation in your screened lanai overlooking premium lush landscaping & There's more than enough room for a pool & you can design the pool how you want it instead of being stuck with someone else's pool design,now you can have your own pool design.Plus during the winter months your pool will get sun from sunrise to sunset because it faces South!Tile in high traffic areas,open concept kitchen and living area floor plan.Easy close access to the best shopping,restaurants,hospitals,emergency services,& easy access to Mid-Cape Bridge to Fort Myers. This home is priced right in the perfect neighborhood.
